CustomField.description:
Defines which scheduled jobs run to set the external id string when the ImportTool_ExternalIdController is invoked. Values are to be comma-separated.
The following values are supported: Assignment Payee Payee Allowance Payee Leave Rule Project Code Timesheet Timesheet Entry
